metadata.name: The Last Marathoner
metadata.description:
THE LAST MARATHONER

Little is known about The Last Marathoner.
It has been said that he has never been tethered to planet earth and that he has traveled far as the sun could see.

May the legend of his journey continue to inspire each and every one of us.

Average Speed: 6:47 per kilometre
Location: Moon

Original Music: @enoebgs

Exploratory #003
